markets.title: Will the independence of the judiciary be weakened during Trump's term?
markets.rules_primary: If 1) an executive order alters the structure of the judiciary, 2) a bill becomes law that undermines judicial independence, or 3) any federal judges are removed outside of the impeachment process, before Jan 20, 2029, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Please see full rules for details on what actions are included in the Payout Criterion.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
